A very powerful meditation that brings peace, love, joy, healing and goodwill to Mother Earth. A form of world service to humanity, it is also aimed at achieving divine consciousness or illumination. &quot;Twin Hearts&quot; refers to the activation of the Heart and Crown chakras, the energy centers associated with human and divine love. This meditation has touched the lives of millions of people. When practiced regularly, some of its benefits are increased mental clarity, psychic abilities, intelligence and comprehension skills.
